# Contributing

This repo is a curated public release. Primary development happens on a
private tree and syncs here, so the public history is intentionally
clean and sparse.

Issues and PRs are welcome. Ground rules:

- Keep it one file: `index.html`. Zero dependencies, zero build step,
  zero network calls. PRs that add any of those will be declined
  regardless of merit.
- ASCII-only source.
- Small, focused PRs over large rewrites.
- By submitting a pull request you agree your contribution is licensed
  under the MIT license of this repository.

Bug reports: include browser + OS, and console output if any.
